HEADWORD: Arabinose
<hw>Ar"a*bin*ose`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>
<def>A sugar of the composition <chform>C5H10O5</chform>, obtained from
cherry gum by boiling it with dilute sulphuric acid.</def>⟦br⟧
